sequenceDiagram
    participant WEB as Web Client
    participant OAUTH as OAuth Provider
    participant BFF as BFF
    participant E as Engine
    participant REG as State Registry
    participant CAM as Camera
    participant MB as Message Broker
    participant EVDB as Evidence DB

    Note over WEB,OAUTH: Authentication
    WEB->>OAUTH: Authorization Request
    OAUTH-->>WEB: Access Token
    WEB->>BFF: Request + Bearer Token
    BFF->>BFF: Validate Token

    Note over E,REG: Initialization (pull config + build registry)
    E->>E: Create EngineStateRegistry
    E->>BFF: GET /api/cameras/engine
    BFF-->>E: Camera configs (connection + frame + observation + decision)
    loop For each camera
        E->>REG: add_camera(config)
        REG->>REG: Create FrameBuffer + StoriesBuffer
    end
    E->>E: Start PreprocessorManager(registry)
    E->>E: Start ProcessingManager(registry)

    Note over WEB,REG: Runtime config change (webhook)
    WEB->>BFF: PUT /api/cameras/:id
    BFF->>BFF: Validate + save to DB
    BFF->>E: POST /config/cameras (webhook)
    alt camera:created
        E->>REG: add_camera(config)
        REG->>REG: Create FrameBuffer + StoriesBuffer
        E->>E: PreprocessorManager.add_camera → start connector
        E->>E: ProcessingManager.add_camera → build VLMProcessor + LLMDetector
    else camera:updated
        E->>REG: update_camera(config)
        REG->>REG: Replace CameraConfig (new ObservationConfig + DecisionConfig)
        E->>E: PreprocessorManager.update_camera → restart connector
        E->>E: ProcessingManager.update_camera → rebuild VLMProcessor + LLMDetector
    else camera:deleted
        E->>REG: remove_camera(camera_id)
        REG->>REG: Dispose FrameBuffer + StoriesBuffer
        E->>E: PreprocessorManager.remove_camera → stop connector
        E->>E: ProcessingManager.remove_camera → evict processor cache
    end
    E-->>BFF: 200 OK { status, cameras }
    BFF-->>WEB: 200 OK (confirmed)

    Note over CAM,EVDB: Event flow with buffering
    loop For each frame batch
        E->>CAM: Connect stream
        CAM-->>E: Frames
        E->>REG: Add frames to camera's FrameBuffer
        E->>REG: Flush camera's FrameBuffer
        REG-->>E: Frames batch
        E->>REG: get_camera(id) → ObservationConfig (model + prompt)
        E->>E: Process batch with VLMProcessor (per-camera model + prompt)
        E->>E: Aggregate descriptions → stories
        E->>REG: Add stories to camera's StoriesBuffer
        E->>REG: Get batch from StoriesBuffer
        REG-->>E: Stories batch
        E->>REG: get_camera(id) → DecisionConfig (model + prompt + output_schema)
        E->>E: Evaluate stories with LLMDetector (per-camera model + structured output)
        alt Event detected
            E->>MB: Publish(event)
            MB->>BFF: Deliver(event)
            BFF->>EVDB: Store evidence
            BFF->>WEB: SSE: event
        end
    end
